data.name: isInstalledRules.Instructions
data.value: Use this form to create, edit, remove, and group rules that determine if this software package is already installed. If you created this update using an MSI or MSP file you will see the automatically generated rule at the installable item level. By default the rules are in an AND group.

data.name: isInstallableRules.Instructions
data.value: Use this form to create, edit, remove, and group rules that determine if this software package can be installed. If you created this update using an MSI or MSP file you will see the automatically generated rule at the installable item level. By default the rules are in an AND group.
